comments: Anthony (ORL) legally contests Murray's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
Carter Jr. (ORL) brings his hand toward Murray (DEN) and marginal contact occurs as Carter Jr. releases away to roll.
Jokic (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball and deflects the pass away from Carter Jr. (ORL).
Murray (DEN) legally contests Wagner's (ORL) post-shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.

Carter Jr. (ORL) briefly grasps Jokic's (DEN) arm/shoulder as he elevates above him and marginal contact occurs as he secures the rebound and dunks the ball. The 24 second shot clock correctly reset after Wagner's (ORL) previously missed shot touches the rim.
Porter Jr. (DEN) grasps and then quickly releases Wagner's (ORL) jersey as the screen is set.
Wagner (ORL) briefly grasps and immediately releases Jokic's (DEN) arm and marginal contact occurs as he uses the screen. Wagner's reaction is not commensurate with the level of contact.
Carter Jr. (ORL) establishes himself in Porter Jr.'s (DEN) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Jokic (DEN) momentarily rests a hand on Wagner's (ORL) body and marginal contact occurs during the driving shot attempt.
Jokic (DEN) and Fultz (ORL) reach for the loose ball and Jokic makes clean hand on ball contact as Fultz is unable to control the rebound.
Jokic (DEN) establishes himself in Fultz's (ORL) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Anthony (ORL) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard an opponent.
Fultz (ORL) grasps and then quickly releases Jokic's (DEN) jersey as marginal contact occurs when they mutually engage off-ball.
Fultz (ORL) initiates illegal contact with Gordon's (DEN) left arm as he attempts to get to the pass.
Murray (DEN) reaches across Fultz (ORL) and makes contact with his arm and body, which affects his SQBR.
Wagner (ORL) legally contests Jokic's (DEN) jump shot attempt.
